The paper focuses on the geometry and algorithms for generating line drawings from 3D models, which is a common topic in computer graphics (cs.GR). The paper also discusses algorithms for extracting contours and computing their visibility, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses hardware-accelerated fast methods, which is a common topic in computer graphics (cs.CG) and machine learning (cs.MM). The paper also includes some novel explanations and implementation tips, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
